                            <comment id="13201307" author="njiang" created="Mon, 6 Feb 2012 14:21:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue is introduced by the enhancement of the XmlConverter to support the stax API better. When turning the Element to a DOMSource, we should create a Document first and then create a DomSource based on the Document.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
